          "description": "Dr. Chung has been my primary doctor for two decades and I've always had a positive experience. He's always explained different issues clearly and helped me with whatever was going on. I trust his medical advice and care. The office is also lovely and in a great location. I've recommended him whenever a friend needs a doctor.\n\nNow that I don't live in NYC anymore, I've come to appreciate him even more! Hence why I'm writing this review now. I found a great PCP where I am now, but establishing GOOD medical care in a new state is challenging and takes a long time. It makes me appreciate so much more the excellent care I've received over the years with my NYC doctors and specialists.",
