          "description": "I love City Care Family Practice! I've been coming here for a couple of years, and what I like most about them is that they're always there when I need them. There aren't many places you can go that have experienced doctors that take last minute appointments, and I appreciate them for that. On top of their flexible availability, the staff is also really great. Front desk always helps with making sure I have everything I need prior to my appointment. Susu is also really great and always makes the process go so smoothl. Dr. Karthik is amazing and knowledgeable and always has the answer to my questions. Harry is new but I've had him a few times and he's awesome",
