          "description": "Susu the nurse was very kind and sweet. Asked me all my general questions about my medical history with patience and took so many vials of blood without me barely noticing the pinch or pain. Harry the PA answered a lot of my questions and concerns since I have not had a medical check up in a few years. He was compassionate when discussing mental health and issues at\nHome affecting my functional mental health state. I will be recommending city care family practice and even considering switching my son care here as well. Thank you to all the caring and accommodating staff for making my first visit so seamless and easy.",
